        <div n="818A703C" type="poem"><head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-818A703C-headnote-1"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-818A703C-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-818A703C-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1"/></lg></head><head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-818A703C-headnote-2"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-818A703C-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-818A703C-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"/></lg></head><head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-818A703C-headnote-3"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-818A703C-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-818A703C-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"/></lg></head>
      <lg n="1" type="stanza"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-818A703C-line-1"> In your Indignation what Mercy appears?&#13;</l><l n="2" xml:id="spp-818A703C-line-2"> While Ionothan's threatn'd with Loss of <del>your</del>his Ears:</l><l n="3" xml:id="spp-818A703C-line-3"> For who woud not think it, a much better Choice;</l><l n="4" xml:id="spp-818A703C-line-4"> By your Knife to be mangled, then wreck'd by y<hi rend="sup">ṛ</hi> Voice:</l><l n="5" xml:id="spp-818A703C-line-5"> If you woud be truly reveng'd on the Parson,</l><l n="6" xml:id="spp-818A703C-line-6"> Command his Attendance while you act the Farce-on:</l><l n="7" xml:id="spp-818A703C-line-7"> Instead of your maiming, your shooting or Banging,</l><l n="8" xml:id="spp-818A703C-line-8"> Bid Povey secure him, while Kite is Haranguing:</l><l n="9" xml:id="spp-818A703C-line-9"> Had this been your Method to torture him, long-since</l><l n="10" xml:id="spp-818A703C-line-10"> He had cut his Own Ears, to be rid of your Nonsense.818A703C   </l></lg></div>
      </div>
